rows.label: qev065205_MSG0002
rows.name: Ah... M-my sisters' voices... Gone silent...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065205_MSG0004
rows.name:
But no... No, that only means we need apply a greater
force to training you. To breaking you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065205_MSG0005
rows.name:
That's how it has always been with each new race of
primitives.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065205_MSG0006
rows.name: You are no different. And you will bow as the rest.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065205_MSG0007
rows.name: This should not be... You are an inferior organism...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065205_MSG0008
rows.name:
We are absolute masters. It is a law of the universe.
Mother told us so![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065205_MSG0009
rows.name: Ahhh... Mother Fortun! Aid your daughters now![ST:wait ]
